*Usage Context: Platform for historical sources and research data for historians and students in historical and archaeological fields.*

*Metadata:*
  * Title: Vue prise sur la terrasse derrière la Cathédrale de Basle (dite Pfalz)
  * Description: This panorama allows viewers to step into the image and become part of the scene. It transforms the perspective that has dominated since the Renaissance, creating a three-dimensional effect that, while impressive, keeps the viewer at a distance from the depicted scene.
  * Date (Extended Date Time Format): 1800
  * Era: 19th Century
  * Creator: Heinrich Bienz Sohn
  * Publisher: [Swiss National Museum](https://www.musée-nationale.ch/de/expositions/2006/1800-1900-basile)
  * Source: [Swiss National Museum, Basel](https://www.musée-nationale.ch/de/expositions/2006/1800-1900-basile)*
